1. U crkvi su se molili da se *demoni* udalje od njih. (In the church, they were praying for the *demons* to leave them.)
2. Njena ljubomora je *demon* koji joj ne da mira. (Her jealousy is a *demon* that doesn't let her have peace.)
3. Ona je *demonstrirala* kako da se koristi novi proizvod. (She *demonstrated* how to use the new product.)
4. Naučnici pokušavaju da *demonstriraju* kako radi njihov eksperiment. (Scientists are trying to *demonstrate* how their experiment works.)
5. U pustinji su videli *demona* koji je plenio životinje. (In the desert, they saw a *demon* that was preying on animals.)
6. Njegovi strahovi su *demonski* i teško ih se oslobađa. (His fears are *demonic* and difficult to overcome.)
7. *Demonstracija* je prošla mirno bez nasilja. (The *demonstration* passed peacefully without violence.)
8. U ovoj sobi se oseća prisustvo *demona*. (In this room, there is a sense of *demonic* presence.)
9. *Demonizacija* političkog protivnika je česta praksa u politici. (The *demonization* of a political opponent is a common practice in politics.)
10. Njegova opsesija je *demon* kojeg nikako ne može da se oslobodi. (His obsession is a *demon* he can't seem to get rid of.)